{
  "texts": [
    "Section 6: Data Privacy and Ethical Considerations Deep learning's use in healthcare poses issues with ethics and privacy.",
    "In order to allay these worries, Vision Saver follows strict security and privacy rules for user data.",
    "Access to the system is limited to licensed healthcare providers, and patient data is anonymised and encrypted to preserve patient privacy.",
    "The transparency and interpretability of the deep learning models are also stressed, ensuring the justification and comprehension of the system's decisions.",
    "Literature Survey[1] Rajalakshmi, R., Subashini, R., Rakshitha, and Sivapriya, R. (2018)."
  ]
}